snippet.title: Best Mae West Quotes that tell a lot about life and women
snippet.description:
Best Mae West Quotes that tell a lot about life and women. These are vivid sayings and quotes from Mae West. The best quotes and aphorisms of Mae West that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Mae West are definitely worth your time.

Mae West was an American stage and film actress, playwright, screenwriter, singer, and sex symbol whose entertainment career spanned over seven decades. She was known for her breezy sexual independence, and her lighthearted bawdy double entendres, often delivered in a husky contralto voice.
